            "reviews": "“A great graphic adventure that will capture fans of role-playing games.”<br>8.2/10 – <a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=https://gamodrome.de/review-the-balled-singer/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >Gamodrome</a><br><br>“The Ballad Singer is a magnificient visual novel! The illustrations are exceptionally beautiful, and we are quickly transported into the world of the game!”<br>8/10 – <a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=https://coupleofgameroff.wixsite.com/coupleofgamer/articles/test-express-steam-the-ballad-singer\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >Couple of Gamer</a><br><br>“We recommend the title to lovers of the RPG genre and graphic adventures and in general to anyone who wants to enjoy in peace a beautiful story told really well.”<br>8.4/10 – <a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=http://www.gamesvillage.it/6910825/the-ballad-singer-recensione/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >Games Village</a><br>",
